WEBVTT

00:01:32.859 --> 00:01:33.793
I'm gonna go look.

00:01:33.860 --> 00:01:34.794
What?

00:01:35.462 --> 00:01:37.330
I'm gonna look for my woman.

00:01:37.497 --> 00:01:39.599
You can look for that other woman.

00:01:44.304 --> 00:01:46.439
Are you dating Julia behind my back?

00:01:48.775 --> 00:01:51.444
I feel like I'm in a confessional...

00:01:51.778 --> 00:01:53.847
Have you had any
experience as a minister?

00:01:54.114 --> 00:01:56.850
You were always the one
leaving others out of the loop.

00:01:58.852 --> 00:02:01.354
We still haven't settled
the score from earlier.

00:02:03.523 --> 00:02:04.524
Any time.

00:02:04.891 --> 00:02:06.192
Lin!

00:02:10.230 --> 00:02:11.764
Hey, out of the way, Lin!

00:02:14.200 --> 00:02:15.135
Lin...

00:02:43.730 --> 00:02:46.666
<i>I was in the same unit</i>
<i>as Vicious on Titan.</i>

00:02:47.834 --> 00:02:49.869
You said that you didn't need comrades...

00:02:51.337 --> 00:02:53.640
but I'm attracted to that word.

00:02:55.174 --> 00:02:56.409
To the point of tears.

00:02:58.411 --> 00:03:00.647
On Titan, we were all comrades.

00:03:52.565 --> 00:03:53.433
What song is that?

00:03:57.670 --> 00:03:58.905
Julia.

00:03:59.672 --> 00:04:00.807
That's a good tune.

00:04:04.344 --> 00:04:07.614
Would you mind if I played that on
my sax when I go home after all this?

00:04:51.557 --> 00:04:54.394
<i>After I came home from the war,</i>
<i>I was imprisoned.</i>

00:04:55.461 --> 00:04:56.996
They suspected that I was a spy.

00:04:57.864 --> 00:04:59.966
I heard that Vicious
testified against me.

00:05:01.968 --> 00:05:05.538
In prison, I went insane from insomnia.

00:05:06.406 --> 00:05:07.974
As a result, I became a drug addict.

00:05:08.408 --> 00:05:09.676
There were side effects.

00:05:09.876 --> 00:05:13.012
My hormonal balance went out of whack,
and this is what happened.

00:05:14.314 --> 00:05:18.818
You're the second person to know
Vicious since I arrived here.

00:05:19.652 --> 00:05:21.654
And the second I've talked
about this to.

00:05:22.689 --> 00:05:24.490
Why are you going to see Vicious?

00:05:25.358 --> 00:05:27.427
Didn't you just say that he framed you?

00:05:28.828 --> 00:05:30.396
I want to see if he really did.

00:05:30.697 --> 00:05:31.698
You're going to die.

00:05:32.365 --> 00:05:33.599
I'm not afraid to die.

00:05:33.666 --> 00:05:34.701
You're lying.

00:05:36.669 --> 00:05:38.471
Either way, I won't last much longer.

00:05:40.740 --> 00:05:42.642
Why did you bring me here?

00:05:45.645 --> 00:05:48.448
Perhaps I wanted to be with someone.

00:05:49.015 --> 00:05:52.418
You selfishly help people,
and bring them along...

00:05:52.919 --> 00:05:54.520
and then you go off to die?

00:06:07.834 --> 00:06:09.836
Are you sure it was this woman?

00:06:10.603 --> 00:06:13.973
Yeah. It's been six months since
I last saw a woman in the flesh,

00:06:14.440 --> 00:06:17.076
and two years since I saw
someone that good looking.

00:06:17.577 --> 00:06:19.112
Of course I wouldn't make a mistake.

00:06:19.912 --> 00:06:22.515
I never wanna live in this town.

00:06:22.682 --> 00:06:25.585
She sat there, and was talking to Gren.

00:06:26.953 --> 00:06:28.988
Julia always sat in that seat, too.

00:06:29.589 --> 00:06:30.590
Julia?

00:06:31.491 --> 00:06:35.828
She suddenly wandered in two years ago,
and disappeared before a month passed.

00:06:36.062 --> 00:06:37.463
What kind of woman was she?

00:06:39.098 --> 00:06:40.767
She was a real babe.

00:06:45.571 --> 00:06:48.174
<i>I'm the only one</i>
<i>that can keep you alive.</i>

00:06:49.575 --> 00:06:52.011
<i>And I'm the only one</i>
<i>that can kill you.</i>

00:06:53.412 --> 00:06:55.915
<i>I'm only watching a dream</i>
<i>that I never awakened from.</i>

00:06:56.749 --> 00:06:58.818
<i>It's like I am watching a dream...</i>

00:06:59.152 --> 00:07:01.621
<i>Be careful when you're with that woman.</i>

00:07:02.655 --> 00:07:04.991
<i>Women are all liars.</i>

00:07:07.059 --> 00:07:09.996
<i>When this is over,</i>
<i>I'm getting out of all this.</i>

00:07:11.631 --> 00:07:13.132
<i>And then, will you come with me?</i>

00:07:16.569 --> 00:07:19.005
<i>Are you going to betray me?</i>

00:07:19.739 --> 00:07:22.708
<i>They're going to kill you.</i>

00:07:23.709 --> 00:07:25.144
<i>Oh, you're finally up.</i>

00:07:25.211 --> 00:07:27.447
<i>You've slept too much.</i>
<i>It's been three days.</i>

00:07:29.949 --> 00:07:32.652
<i>Your left eye and right eye</i>
<i>are different colors.</i>

00:07:33.486 --> 00:07:35.588
<i>My left eye sees the past...</i>

00:07:36.022 --> 00:07:38.624
<i>Then what about your right eye?</i>

00:07:54.740 --> 00:07:56.209
I'm not dead.

00:08:11.591 --> 00:08:12.925
Which way is west?

00:08:16.629 --> 00:08:17.763
Thanks.

00:08:23.002 --> 00:08:26.138
Tranquilizer, huh?
They're mocking me.

00:08:53.933 --> 00:08:56.569
Sorry, but can I ask you something?

00:08:56.969 --> 00:08:59.205
Where is a blue apartment
building called Orlando?

00:08:59.272 --> 00:09:01.941
Don't ask me! I don't know anything!

00:09:02.608 --> 00:09:03.776
Come on.

00:09:04.544 --> 00:09:07.680
I want nothing to do
with foreigners from now on.

00:09:07.747 --> 00:09:09.148
I'm just asking!

00:09:10.316 --> 00:09:12.618
I'm gonna go find an honest job.

00:09:18.257 --> 00:09:19.892
What the hell?

00:09:27.667 --> 00:09:28.768
It's here.

00:09:56.996 --> 00:09:57.863
Hey!

00:09:58.164 --> 00:09:59.332
Hey, get it together!

00:10:03.369 --> 00:10:04.270
Jet?

00:10:04.837 --> 00:10:06.305
What the hell are you doing?

00:10:08.908 --> 00:10:09.942
What's all this about?

00:10:10.343 --> 00:10:12.612
He was one of those kinds of guys?

00:10:13.245 --> 00:10:14.680
What are you saying?

00:10:14.880 --> 00:10:17.783
Gren isn't like that.

00:10:18.351 --> 00:10:19.785
Gren?

00:10:25.124 --> 00:10:26.993
"Mangan" with "ura-dora."

00:10:28.127 --> 00:10:30.029
He's using an ancient code.

00:10:34.000 --> 00:10:37.036
Julia was here... in this town.

00:10:41.807 --> 00:10:42.675
<i>Yo.</i>

00:10:43.075 --> 00:10:44.010
Yeah?

00:10:44.076 --> 00:10:45.411
<i>Got anything?</i>

00:10:45.678 --> 00:10:46.412
None.

00:10:46.679 --> 00:10:48.014
<i>I got something good.</i>

00:10:48.080 --> 00:10:49.382
Catch them yourself.

00:10:50.016 --> 00:10:52.351
I know about the guy
from that code name "Julia."

00:10:52.985 --> 00:10:54.353
<i>It's a guy named Gren.</i>

00:10:54.887 --> 00:10:56.222
<i>He's an escaped convict</i>

00:10:56.288 --> 00:10:58.791
and has a hefty bounty on his head.

00:10:58.858 --> 00:11:00.126
If you catch him,

00:11:00.192 --> 00:11:01.761
<i>I'll let you back on.</i>

00:11:13.672 --> 00:11:14.673
Hello?

00:11:15.141 --> 00:11:16.375
<i>I'm overhead.</i>

00:11:17.143 --> 00:11:20.146
<i>Come to the roof of the building</i>
<i>closest to the sky.</i>

00:11:20.780 --> 00:11:22.448
I'll send a woman over.

00:11:23.182 --> 00:11:24.183
<i>I don't care.</i>

00:11:24.784 --> 00:11:27.386
<i>Although I would have</i>
<i>liked to see you as well.</i>

00:11:31.390 --> 00:11:33.392
You broke the Bebop,

00:11:33.926 --> 00:11:37.696
but kept the Swordfish
and Hammerhead mobile.

00:11:37.963 --> 00:11:40.800
Did you leave that message
so that we'd come find you?

00:11:41.434 --> 00:11:43.135
You've got to be kidding.

00:11:43.736 --> 00:11:45.404
Were you just testing us?

00:11:46.772 --> 00:11:47.940
Why did you come here?

00:11:48.808 --> 00:11:49.875
I want my money back.

00:11:50.376 --> 00:11:51.377
The safe...

00:11:52.812 --> 00:11:54.480
only had 20,000 in it.

00:11:55.081 --> 00:11:56.248
Is that so?

00:11:56.782 --> 00:11:57.783
Dummy.

00:11:58.951 --> 00:12:01.754
Hey. Who is Julia?

00:12:02.254 --> 00:12:06.192
I don't know. But she has
something to do with Spike.

00:12:06.759 --> 00:12:08.160
That's all I know.

00:12:34.120 --> 00:12:36.455
Souvenir, souvenir, is it here yet?

00:13:20.533 --> 00:13:23.269
It has an EX+ ranking. It's real.

00:13:23.502 --> 00:13:24.436
Hand it over.

00:13:27.039 --> 00:13:29.441
This is the Titan Opal
that you requested.

00:13:30.876 --> 00:13:33.112
Give Gren my regards.

00:13:35.347 --> 00:13:37.416
You saved me from that scorpion back then.

00:13:38.384 --> 00:13:40.386
Yet you sold me out.

00:14:00.339 --> 00:14:01.607
Gren?

00:14:03.175 --> 00:14:04.176
Long time no see.

00:14:04.944 --> 00:14:06.078
What are you up to?

00:14:06.612 --> 00:14:09.181
You gave me that music box
because you...

00:14:09.515 --> 00:14:12.351
never thought I'd take
it apart and examine it?

00:14:13.352 --> 00:14:15.087
You found the transmitter.

00:14:15.521 --> 00:14:17.122
Julia was the one who found it.

00:14:18.190 --> 00:14:21.460
She realized as soon as she heard
it was a gift from you.

00:14:22.127 --> 00:14:23.562
And what about it?

00:14:24.930 --> 00:14:27.066
Are you trying to kill me again?

00:14:29.068 --> 00:14:30.536
We fought in the war together.

00:14:31.503 --> 00:14:33.038
We were comrades.

00:14:36.342 --> 00:14:40.412
We fought together
on that desert battlefield.

00:14:42.982 --> 00:14:44.183
I looked up to you.

00:14:47.253 --> 00:14:48.988
I believed in you.

00:14:53.225 --> 00:14:55.194
There is nothing there to believe.

00:14:56.996 --> 00:14:58.430
Nor is there a need to believe.

00:15:01.500 --> 00:15:02.468
Sir Vicious!

00:15:21.654 --> 00:15:24.156
In this world,
there is nothing to believe in.

00:15:32.598 --> 00:15:33.532
Vicious!

00:15:36.168 --> 00:15:40.339
Lin's soul won't be saved since he lost
his life protecting someone like you!

00:15:41.173 --> 00:15:42.975
I'm not what he was protecting!

00:15:43.409 --> 00:15:44.543
He protected the rules!

00:16:05.631 --> 00:16:06.565
You're in the way!

00:17:44.496 --> 00:17:46.198
Hey! Come on, get a grip! Hey!

00:17:46.799 --> 00:17:49.201
Where is Julia?
Where did she go?

00:17:52.504 --> 00:17:53.772
Do you know her?

00:17:54.640 --> 00:17:56.708
Where is she now?

00:18:03.515 --> 00:18:04.817
He hit some vital organs.

00:18:06.118 --> 00:18:09.188
Shit, would an ambulance
come to a place like this?

00:18:13.592 --> 00:18:17.429
Can you lift me up into the pod again?

00:18:19.331 --> 00:18:20.833
I want to go to Titan.

00:18:21.433 --> 00:18:23.368
You can't possibly last
in your condition!

00:18:23.435 --> 00:18:24.870
It would take too long!

00:18:25.737 --> 00:18:28.440
I won't last long anyway.

00:18:28.841 --> 00:18:31.443
Dying during the voyage
would be a good way to go.

00:18:32.444 --> 00:18:36.515
I want to return there...
one more time.

00:18:37.749 --> 00:18:39.885
I want to be as close as I can.

00:18:40.552 --> 00:18:41.787
Please.

00:18:55.367 --> 00:18:56.435
I see.

00:18:57.836 --> 00:18:59.371
You are Spike.

00:19:00.606 --> 00:19:02.808
Julia was always talking about you.

00:19:03.775 --> 00:19:06.678
That your two eyes were
of different colors.

00:19:07.412 --> 00:19:08.714
That's what she said.

00:19:09.648 --> 00:19:13.752
That you get a strange feeling
when you look into his eyes.

00:19:15.154 --> 00:19:16.321
What was she doing?

00:19:17.523 --> 00:19:20.926
In the corner seat of the bar.

00:19:22.161 --> 00:19:25.264
She always sat there
while I wasn't paying attention.

00:19:26.698 --> 00:19:28.233
She always requested...

00:19:28.300 --> 00:19:30.269
the same song...

00:19:31.270 --> 00:19:32.337
...and smiled.

00:19:34.339 --> 00:19:35.774
Sadly...

00:19:36.708 --> 00:19:37.943
smiled.

00:20:47.246 --> 00:20:48.447
What do you have?

00:20:48.814 --> 00:20:49.715
<i>Nothing.</i>

00:20:51.583 --> 00:20:53.852
<i>Hurry up and get in. We're taking off.</i>

00:21:04.763 --> 00:21:05.631
Julia.

00:21:06.365 --> 00:21:07.332
What?

00:21:07.399 --> 00:21:10.802
Nothing. Just an adult's idle muttering.

00:21:11.536 --> 00:21:13.338
Where did all of you guys go?

00:21:13.772 --> 00:21:14.840
Someplace good.

00:21:15.374 --> 00:21:17.009
Ed's the only one left out!

00:21:17.509 --> 00:21:19.478
I'll tell you someday.

00:21:20.879 --> 00:21:22.614
Nah, it's okay, really.

00:21:23.649 --> 00:21:25.617
You're not being cute.

00:21:41.967 --> 00:21:43.969
The star fell, Bull.

00:21:44.803 --> 00:21:47.306
That is no ordinary star.

00:21:47.606 --> 00:21:49.408
That is the tear of a warrior.

00:21:49.875 --> 00:21:51.476
What is a warrior?

00:21:51.877 --> 00:21:55.714
One who has finished his battle
somewhere on this planet.

00:21:58.016 --> 00:22:03.322
A pitiful soul that could
not believe in the Great Spirit.

00:24:11.917 --> 00:24:14.186
<i>What is going on with this world?</i>

00:24:14.452 --> 00:24:16.588
<i>In life, darkness looms</i>
<i>one inch away from you.</i>

00:24:16.655 --> 00:24:19.224
<i>This world is truly full of mistakes.</i>

00:24:19.491 --> 00:24:24.729
<i>In that case, we'll step</i>
<i>away from the mainstream...</i>

00:24:25.463 --> 00:24:27.165
<i>and lead the life of a dropout.</i>

00:24:27.232 --> 00:24:29.868
<i>A psychedelic rhapsody</i>
<i>for someone just like you.</i>

00:24:29.935 --> 00:24:33.505
<i>Next episode: "Bohemian Rhapsody."</i>

00:24:33.939 --> 00:24:38.510
<i>Now, won't you waste</i>
<i>away your life with us?</i>

